flowRoot.flowPara: 2 bullet points for reward of grasp and reward of gaze

Biological systems have been known to achieve near optimal decision making when faced with noisy sensory and motor systems. In such a scenario, we investigate how optimal behaviour can be trained through positive and negative feedback.
